source.name: Global Earth Observation Integrated Data Environment's Unified Access Framework for Environmental Data
source.description: NOAA's Global Earth Observation - Integrated Data Environment (GEO-IDE) is framework for engaging NOAA's environmental data management communities through sharing expertise, experience, and information.  UAF is a NOAA-wide effort to make environmental datasets easy to find and use. It is an important contribution to realizing the vision of NOAA's Global Earth Observation - Integrated Data Environment (GEO-IDE) Initiative.
